trans-unit.source: Represents the exception that is thrown when you try to access a printer using printer settings that are not valid.
trans-unit.target: Representerer unntak som er et når du prøver å få tilgang til en skriver med skriverinnstillinger som ikke er gyldig.

trans-unit.source: The most common cause of printer settings that are not valid is referencing a printer that does not exist.
trans-unit.target: Den vanligste årsaken til skriverinnstillinger som ikke er gyldig refererer til en skriver som ikke finnes.

trans-unit.source: For more information about printing, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om utskrift av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>Oversikt over navneområde.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.InvalidPrinterException"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.InvalidPrinterException"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings"></xref> that specifies the settings for a printer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings"> </xref> som angir innstillingene for en skriver.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.InvalidPrinterException"></xref> class with serialized data.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.InvalidPrinterException"> </xref> klasse serialiserte dataene.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is called during deserialization to reconstitute the exception object transmitted over a stream.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren kalles under deserialisering til reconstitute unntak objektet overføres via en dataflyt.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> that holds the serialized object data about the exception being thrown.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> som inneholder den serialiserte objektdata om som oppstod et unntak.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext> that contains contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>som inneholder kontekstavhengig informasjon om kilden eller målet.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>

trans-unit.source: The class name is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> or <xref:System.Exception.HResult*> is 0.
trans-unit.target: Klassenavnet er <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> eller <xref:System.Exception.HResult*>er 0.</xref:System.Exception.HResult*>

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> with information about the exception.
trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> med informasjon om unntaket.

trans-unit.source: The GetObjectData method sets a <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> with all the exception object data targeted for serialization.
trans-unit.target: GetObjectData metoden angir en <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>med alle objektet unntaksdataene mål for serialisering.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>

trans-unit.source: During deserialization, the exception is reconstituted from the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> transmitted over the stream.
trans-unit.target: Under deserialisering, reconstituted unntaket fra den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>overføres via dataflyten.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> that holds the serialized object data about the exception being thrown.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> som inneholder den serialiserte objektdata om som oppstod et unntak.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext> that contains contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>som inneholder kontekstavhengig informasjon om kilden eller målet.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>
